<HEADLINE> Greece's Inflation Remains at 2.1 Percent in July </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ATHENS, August 6 (Xinhua) -- Greece's inflation rate remained
at 2.1 percent in July this year, according to the National
Statistics Service (NSS) Friday.
</P>
<P>
