<TEXT>
<P>
HARARE, August 7 (Xinhua) -- Representatives of the Zimbabwe
Congress of Trade Union (ZCTU) Saturday unanimously voted for the
adoption of the declaration of the National Working Peoples
Convention, wishing to form a labor party.
</P>
<P>
