confirmed that the Russian Central Bank has over the past few
years secretly transferred part of its aid fund to an obscure
offshore company in the British island of Jersey in the English
Channel, which was described as a "fiscal paradise." The leaders
of the Russian Central Bank realized tremendous personal benefits
through the embezzlement, in which the Russian government was kept
in total darkness.
</P>
